Babe London https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Babe_London 0 Babe London (born Ruth Glover, August 28, 1901 – November 29, 1980) was an American actress and comedian, most remembered for her onetime-only partnership with Oliver Hardy, in the 1931's Laurel and Hardy's two-reeler Our Wife.
